url: "https://www.thesovereignmechanica.ai/"
abstract: >
  TSM79 is an inline AI control plane that sits between an application and
  every model it talks to. Each request is evaluated before it leaves the
  perimeter: PII is detected and redacted, secrets are blocked, the request
  is routed by policy, and the whole event is committed to a tamper-evident
  audit ledger. The architecture is polyglot — Rust on the hot path, Python
  for ML escalation, Go for control plane and the sovereign-overlay DHT,
  Java for operator REST, C# for the policy DSL language server, C++ for
  the Wasm edge worker host, and eBPF/XDP for kernel-level packet authority.
  It also defines a self-certifying name layer (.tsm) that governs overlay
  content through the same firewall.
